summary: Patches to maintain compatibility between Revenge of the Enemies and other popular mods.
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#9900ff][size=6][center][/center][center]Revenge of the Enemies Patches[/center][/size][/color][/b][b] [/b]
[size=3][b]Various patches to maintain compatibility between Revenge of the Enemies (Rebirth Monster) and other popular mods.[/b][/size]

[center][b]Revenge of the Enemies [/b][i]by MyEvergreenHometown[/i][b] [/b]
[color=#5ea2e5][u][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40491/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40491/?[/url][/u][/color][/center]
[b][size=4]
[i]There are 24 patches currently available for the following mods:[/i] [/size][/b]
[b]

Unofficial Skyrim Legendary Edition Patch (USLEEP) [/b][i]by Arthmoor
[/i][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71214/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71214/?[/url]

[b]Organized Bandits In Skyrim (OBIS) and OBIS Dragonborn (OBISDB) [/b][i]by Indigoblade and the OBIS Team[/i]

[size=3][b]I have also uploaded custom merged patches of some of these that reduce the number of plugins necessary.[/b][/size]

[center][size=3][b][color=#1e84cc]Personal thanks and kudos to users [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/6634188]ttannatt[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/5397430]mikegray[/url] & [url=http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/user/31310890-clioshand/]clioshand[/url] for their generous donations.  [/color][color=#f4f4f4]:)[/color][/b][/size][/center]
